## 10. Maintenance and Updates

### 10.1 When Figma Changes

1. Update CSS variables in `app/globals.css`
2. Update design analysis documentation
3. Test affected components for breaking changes
4. Update this rules document if patterns change

### 10.2 Adding New Components

1. Review Figma design and extract design tokens
2. Create design analysis document
3. Implement using shadcn/ui primitives
4. Apply design tokens via CSS variables
5. Test responsively across all breakpoints
6. Document any accepted deviations

### 10.3 Design System Evolution

- **Versioning**: Track major design system changes in documentation
- **Migration**: Create migration guides when design tokens change significantly
- **Communication**: Update team when design patterns evolve

