## 11. Journey Page — Responsive Rules

*Source: Figma node 15992:29537*

### 11.1 Container & Gutters

Same global side padding tiers apply:
- xl/2xl: 80px (5rem)
- md/lg: 32px (2rem)
- xs/sm: 28px (1.75rem)

### 11.2 Layout Mode Switch

- `< xl`: compact/stacked layout
- `≥ xl`: desktop grid layout

### 11.3 Section Behavior Rules

**Hero**:
- `≥ xl`: 2-column (copy left + illustration right)
- `< xl`: stacked (copy first, illustration secondary)
- xs/sm: use shorter helper text — no truncation

**Toolkit Cards**:
- Consistent padding + button placement across breakpoints
- Allow CTA button to drop below text on small screens (never overlap)

**FAQ**:
- Accordion rows must have large tap targets (min 44×44px)
- Define default expanded/collapsed state in implementation

**How BizWiz Works**:
- `≥ xl`: 2-column layout
- `< xl`: stacked

**Helpful Links**:
- `≥ xl`: 2-up card grid
- `< xl`: 1-up stacked

